<L>__{exterior upper east side same}
<A>__{from amid the rush of traffic, a taxi breaks free and glides to the curb in front of the restaurant. its facade is windowless. only a small brass plaque on the grey marble reveals that this is elysium. wills and eriko, 30's, japanese, aloof and stunning, emerge from the taxi, elegantly dressed, and move to the front door.}
